data.description: Open House Nov 4th 11-1pm! Welcome to McAlister Place town homes! Rare 3 bedroom available for you to move right in & enjoy maintenance free living. Feel the lovely flow with 2 story living room & enjoy the warmth from your gas log fireplace this Holiday Season with temperatures already there! Bright and airy are the best words to describe this home as you will absolutely love the bamboo wood floors throughout and fresh tile in bathrooms! Open kitchen overlooks main den area & leads to quaint patio for extra living space & fun grilling! Primary bedroom boasts space with cathedral ceiling and awesome garden tub in primary bath is perfecto for R&R! Washer & Dryer included for instant savings! Walk to the neighborhood pool easily to relax or meet neighbors! Tons of shopping and restaurants within 2 miles and only 3.5 miles from PTI Airport and Honda Jet. Enjoy 8 mile drive to downtown Greensboro! Major highways 1 mile away. Did I mention the 1 car garage-WOW this one has it all!
